92static int
93get_type(const char *name, const char *list[], unsigned len)
94{
95 unsigned i;
96 for (i = 0; i < len; i++)
97 if (list[i] && strcasecmp(list[i], name) == 0)
98 return i;
99 return -1;
100}
101
102#define SIZEOF_ARRAY(a) (sizeof((a))/sizeof((a)[0]))
103
104const char *
105der_get_class_name(unsigned num)
106{
107 if (num >= SIZEOF_ARRAY(class_names))
108 return NULL;
109 return class_names[num];
110}
111
112int
113der_get_class_num(const char *name)
114{
115 return get_type(name, class_names, SIZEOF_ARRAY(class_names));
116}
117
118const char *
119der_get_type_name(unsigned num)
120{
121 if (num >= SIZEOF_ARRAY(type_names))
122 return NULL;
123 return type_names[num];
124}
125
126int
127der_get_type_num(const char *name)
128{
129 return get_type(name, type_names, SIZEOF_ARRAY(type_names));
130}
131
132const char *
133der_get_tag_name(unsigned num)
134{
135 if (num >= SIZEOF_ARRAY(tag_names))
136 return NULL;
137 return tag_names[num];
138}
139
140int
141der_get_tag_num(const char *name)
142{
143 return get_type(name, tag_names, SIZEOF_ARRAY(tag_names));
144}
